_sText: This map is a remake of a CS 1.6 map originally created by Spuoces i remade the map completely from scratch, i have added a lot to the map from the original cs version. It was a great map in 1.6 and still is in source. Changes/Additions - the sizes of some areas have changed a bit - i have added a landscape instead - i have added a lot more detail to the water as well as the landscape - it has displacements almost every where you look - there is a shark that swims through the water - the ladder in t spawn is not a rope ladder - t spawn is a lot different - i added a lot more detail to the beach Fun Facts - you can get onto the fishing boats - the shark will eventually kill you - you can get onto the roof of the main building as well as the little shack - there are indeed buy zones they are on the floating platforms - 20 spawn points - have fun ! If you come across any bugs or things you would like changed let me know. I may make a version 2 with a custom tuned nav file, possibly with more sharks and maybe even birds in the sky as well as more spawn points.
